{"tid":1962858,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"曱甴車喺停機坪被鎖轆 機管局劃位改為警甴專用","createTime":"2020-04-07T18:00:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T19:45:15.000Z","uid":204539,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e52b90227eb75ae4bcd02be0e966d418c07dd324","tid":1962858,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T18:00:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200407/large/1586249438_0821.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200407%2Flarge%2F1586249438_0821.jpg&h=221fa355&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200407/WPP6TAXLDTKCAVXI36UGO55DAQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200407%2FWPP6TAXLDTKCAVXI36UGO55DAQ%2F&d=BHyrWEjohbhGCquuSPOYYjFPTz8k007NAABMmnbcnzw%3D&h=1c241d8d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200407%2FWPP6TAXLDTKCAVXI36UGO55DAQ%2F&h=f1669348\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200407/WPP6TAXLDTKCAVXI36UGO55DAQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n上月網上流傳一張警車被鎖車圖，地點為香港國際機場停機坪禁區，有機管局職員發現該車輛涉違泊，即決定鎖車。事後機管局稱經調查後發現涉事警車當時正執行職務，稱鎖車的職員在執行程序上「有偏差」。事件發展半個多月，今日（7日）網上再流傳同一地點圖片，相中警車被鎖車位置，地上已劃線列為警方及入境事務處專用泊車位。<br />\n<br />\n相片在機場情報group流傳，網民批評：「軍政府當權，只要佢哋鍾意，跑道都畀個位佢。」、「咁下次海關俾人鎖車，之後又會唔會加多個名喺地下㗎？」<br />\n<br />\n本報向機管局求證相片真偽時，機管局沒有直接回應，只稱現時機管局附例中有關停泊車位規則，賦予執法人員在執勤時的相關豁免，機管局亦會不時檢討禁區車輛及地勤設施於停機坪停放的位置及標示，進行改善。"},{"pid":"8a87eb34267212f939d7bafb7979b1a94a12e684","tid":1962858,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T18:13:33.000Z","msg":"機管局under Hong Kong popo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d38c0784af900ab493ed47c5fbae83b558659d3","tid":1962858,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T19:02:31.000Z","msg":"機管局呢啲平時都奶到雪雪聲"},{"pid":"f19a39f7efa67db3d6a2359